au.org.intersect.dms.core.service
Interface Ingestor

All Known Implementing Classes:
CellRIngestor, ImmediateCopyIngestor, InPlaceIngestor, MicroCTIngestor
public interface Ingestor

Dataset ingestor for instrument data. Encapsulates different ingestion strategies and allows to ingest data from different instrument different way.

void stopIngest(Long jobId)

Parameters:
jobId - ingestion job ID

startIngest

boolean startIngest(Long jobId)
Method to notify ingestor that ingestion is about to start. After this method is called files processing happens. This callback method is usefull for polling ingestions. Ingestor implementation should return true if ingestion should happen and false if ingestion was cancelled

Parameters:
jobId - ingestion job ID
Returns:
true if ingestion should "go" or false if it was canceled
